UE5 Blueprint File - BP_NPC_Spawner_v01
========================================

This is a Blueprint Actor that spawns NPCs in the world.

To create this blueprint in Unreal Engine 5.2+:
1. Right-click in Content Browser
2. Search for "Actor"
3. Select "BP_NPC_Spawner_v01"
4. Click "Create"

Components:
- SpawnZone (BoxComponent)
- SpawnPoint (SceneComponent)
- NPCReference (ObjectProperty)
- CurrentPopulation (Integer)
- MaxPopulation (Integer)
- SpawnRate (Float)
- IsEnabled (Boolean)

Functions:
- SpawnNPC(ENPCRole, FVector)
- DespawnNPC(ANPC_Base*)
- UpdatePopulation(float)
- GetSpawnPool(ENPCDistrict, float) -> DT_NPC_SpawnPool
- GetPopulation() -> Integer
- SetMaxPopulation(Integer)
- SetSpawnRate(Float)
- EnableSpawner(Boolean)

Note: This blueprint must be compiled after adding components.
Note: This blueprint requires spawn pool data assets from designers.
Note: This blueprint requires NPC blueprints from 3D artists.